This is my son.This is his first year playing organized baseball.Hes got a lot going for him.Hes a lefty and hits from either side of the plate with authority. He is his father's son in every way on the ball field. Natural talent,aggressive and determined.Very eager to learn.Ill make sure as his father - coach that he will be granted every opportunity to shine the way I know he will.﻿
